  "detailed_description": "Tiamat’s Drink is a hardcore vertical shoot ’em up roguelike game inspired by the 16-bit era consoles. Fight against powerful enemies, defeat unique bosses, unlock challenging levels and obtain extra powers! <br><br>So get ready and don't forget to enjoy our exclusive soundtrack!<br><br><br><strong>Features:</strong><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>24 Zones levels.<br></li><li>9 Boss Battles.<br></li><li>Unique music designed for each level and boss.<br></li><li>Random enemies through levels.<br></li><li>Unique generated dungeon levels.<br></li><li>Great replay value.<br></li><li>Well-designed learning curve.<br></li><li>Great Soundtrack including 30+ pieces of music.<br></li><li>Multiplayer local co-op.</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1203780/extras/63d607582177d1d36d018667492a142d.poster.avif?t=1591381719\" width=532 height=666 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1203780/extras/63d607582177d1d36d018667492a142d.webm?t=1591381719\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1203780/extras/63d607582177d1d36d018667492a142d.mp4?t=1591381719\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
